
### .gitignore

```gitignore
# Node.js
node_modules/
npm-debug.log
yarn-error.log
package-lock.json      # Optional: keep if you prefer npm over yarn
yarn.lock              # Optional: keep if you prefer yarn over npm

# Build / dist
dist/
build/

# Logs
*.log
logs/
*.log.*

# Environment / secrets
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# Editor / OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

# Temporary files
*.swp
*~
*.bak
*.tmp

# Test artifacts (if you add tests later)
coverage/